o they can be recognized as links by anything parsing the help text.\r\n\r\n<!--\r\nChecklist:\r\n- Read the [Contributing Guidelines](https://github.com/python/mypy/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md)\r\n- Add tests for all changed behaviour.\r\n- If you can't add a test, please explain why and how you verified your changes work.\r\n- Make sure CI passes.\r\n- Please do not force push to the PR once it has been reviewed.\r\n-->\r\n\r\nIn lieu of a test, here's a complete diff between the `--help` output of the `master` branch and this PR (formatting for 80-column width):\r\n\r\n```diff\r\n--- /tmp/old_help.out\t2025-09-11 14:50:05.691931971 -0400\r\n+++ /tmp/new_help.out\t2025-09-11 14:49:38.325378770 -0400\r\n@@ -128,8 +128,7 @@\r\n None and Optional handling:\r\n   Adjust how values of type 'None' are handled. For more context on how mypy\r\n   handles values of type 'None', see:\r\n-  https://mypy.readthedocs.io/en/stable/kinds_of_types.html#optional-types-\r\n-  and-the-none-type\r\n+  https://mypy.readthedocs.io/en/stable/kinds_of_types.html#optional-types-and-the-none-type\r\n \r\n   --implicit-optional       Assume arguments with default values of None are\r\n                             Optional (inverse: --no-implicit-optional)\r\n@@ -224,7 +223,7 @@\r\n   Adjust how mypy incrementally type checks and caches modules. Mypy caches\r\n   type information about modules into a cache to let you speed up future\r\n   invocations of mypy. Also see mypy's daemon mode:\r\n-  mypy.readthedocs.io/en/stable/mypy_daemon.html#mypy-daemon\r\n+  https://mypy.readthedocs.io/en/stable/mypy_daemon.html#mypy-daemon\r\n \r\n   --no-incremental          Disable module cache (inverse: --incremental)\r\n   --cache-dir DIR           Store module cache info in the given folder in\r\n@@ -284,7 +283,7 @@\r\n \r\n Running code:\r\n   Specify the code you want to type check. For more details, see\r\n-  mypy.readthedocs.io/en/stable/running_mypy.html#running-mypy\r\n+  https://mypy.readthedocs.io/en/stable/running_mypy.html#running-mypy\r\n \r\n   --explicit-package-bases  Use current directory and MYPYPATH to determine\r\n                             module names of files passed (inverse: --no-\r\n\r\n```\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/python/mypy/issues/19825/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/python/mypy/issues/19825/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"id":19665962555,"node_id":"SE_lADOAGuhRc7KrJETzwAAAASULsY7","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/python/mypy/issues/events/19665962555","actor":{"login":"aprilwin1771983-a11y","id":231835693,"node_id":"U_kgDODdGILQ","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/231835693?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/aprilwin1771983-a11y","html_url":"https://github.com/aprilwin1771983-a11y","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aprilwin1771983-a11y/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aprilwin1771983-a11y/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aprilwin1771983-a11y/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aprilwin1771983-a11y/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aprilwin1771983-a11y/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aprilwin1771983-a11y/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aprilwin1771983-a11y/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aprilwin1771983-a11y/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aprilwin1771983-a11y/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"event":"subscribed","commit_id":null,"commit_url":null,"created_at":"2025-09-12T17:34:45Z","performed_via_github_app":null},{"id":20685769101,"node_id":"REFE_lADOAGuhRc7KrJETzwAAAATQ98mN","url":"https://api.github.com/